references: Related: CF 275794, Ord 91433, Ord 91843. Superseding: Ord 100617, Ord 100899.
summary: AN ORDINANCE relating to the Department of Parks and Recreation and that certain real estate contract (Lake Union Park site) between The City of Seattle and Washington Natural Gas Company authorized by Ordinances 91433 and 91843, authorizing execution of an agreement relating thereto; authorizing acceptance of a Special Warranty Deed to said property; authorizing disbursement of the final payment on said contract; and partially superseding Ordinances 100617 and 100899.
